Package: fingwit
Architecture: all
Depends: python3,
         python3-gi,
         python3-setproctitle,
         gir1.2-xapp-1.0 (>= 2.5.0),
         libpam-fprintd,
         ${misc:Depends},
         libpam-fingwit (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Fingerprint Configuration Tool
 Utility application used to configure fingerprint authentication.

Package: libpam-fingwit
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends},
         python3,
         python3-gi,
         fprintd
Description: Smart PAM module for fingerprint authentication
 This PAM module provides intelligent fingerprint authentication
 that automatically:
 .
  * Skips fingerprint auth for users with encrypted home directories
    during login (but allows it for sudo/unlock)
  * Avoids interference with SSH sessions
  * Falls back gracefully when hardware is unavailable
 .
 The module is self-contained with embedded Python logic for
 complex detection and D-Bus communication with fprintd.

Package: libpam-fingwit-dbg
Section: debug
Priority: extra
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Pre-Depends: ${misc:Pre-Depends}
Depends: libpam-fingwit (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: libpam-fingwit library - debug symbols
 This package contains the symbols files needed to debug the fingwit pam module.
